00:33:37.600 --> 00:33:39.279
They had a choice to be made.

00:33:39.279 --> 00:33:41.360
There was a choice to be made.

00:33:41.400 --> 00:33:45.120
Even as we find that Joshua would say

00:33:45.120 --> 00:33:46.680
at the end of the book of Joshua,

